## Technology-Specific Notes

### React + Rails Integration
- Rails serves API at /api
- React dev server proxies API requests
- Production: serve React build from Rails public/

### Common Gotchas
- CORS issues â†’ check initializers/cors.rb
- Type mismatches â†’ sync frontend types with serializers
- Auth tokens â†’ use interceptors, not manual headers
- N+1 queries â†’ use includes in Rails controllers
- console.log in production â†’ remove all debugging statements

